msgid ""
"All [units](../units/index.md) have the following statistics shown on their "
"cards."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/keywords/combat.md docs/units/index.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Symbol | Name | Meaning |\n"
"| :---: | :--- | :--- |\n"
"| :attack: | Attack | How much damage this unit will deal to another unit. |\n"
"| :defense: | Defense | Decreases the damage received from non-magical sources â€” damage received cannot be less than 0. |\n"
"| :health_points: | Health Points | How much damage this unit can receive, before being removed from Combat. |\n"
"| :initiative: | Initiative | How fast the unit is. Higher number means they'll get to activate sooner in Combat. |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: docs/keywords/combat.md
