msgid "Damage"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/keywords/combat.md
msgid "Also shown as :damage:."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: docs/keywords/combat.md
msgid ""
"Should a [unit](../units/index.md) receive damage from any source, it will "
"be subtracted from its [health points](combat.md#statistics) directly. The "
"[defense value](combat.md#statistics) only reduces the [attack value]"
"(combat.md#statistics) of the attacking [unit](../units/index.md), but not "
"the damage received of the [unit](../units/index.md) that is being attacked."
msgstr ""

