#. type: Plain text
#: docs/keywords/combat.md docs/keywords/obstacle.md
msgid ""
"Any space that is occupied by a [unit](../units/index.md), an obstacle "
"marker, a Wall or a Gate may not be stepped on.  [Flying units](../units/"
"index.md#flying-units) may move through these spaces, but their movement is "
"not allowed to end in such a space."
msgstr ""
